      <title>特朗普承诺制造繁荣。行业不太确定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-05/trump-promised-a-manufacturing-boom-industries-are-not-so-sure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统誓言他的历史性关税闪电战（Blitz）会恢复国内制造业，但行业担心他的方法正在引起人们对他是否可以兑现经济繁荣的承诺的新怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-05/trump-promised-a-manufacturing-boom-industries-are-not-so-sure</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Apr 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
